OCR by ScanR
Compiled for unix systems in C99

Parameters:
first parameter should be a path to an image.

Accepted parameters:

binarization: -b -bin
contrast down: -cdown -contrastdown
contrast up: -cup -contrastup
grayscale: -g -grayscale
noise reduction: -n -noise
Waiting for input: -w -wait
Complete segmentation using method 1: -s -seg
Complete segmentation using method 2: -s2 -seg2
Neural network showcase: -XOR
Show the current image: -show

For every complete operation the result is stored in result.png in images/